name: As a Admin User, I can create multiple user with Array

testSteps.description: 1: As a Admin User, I can create multiple user with Array ({beforUpdate=testuser1, afterUpdate=testuser2})

children.description:
Given I provide below user information to create array
| id | userName | firstname | lastname | email | password | phoneNumber | userStatus |
| 20 | testuser1 | firstname | lastname | testuser@gmail.com | test123 | 123456789 | 0 |
| 21 | testuser2 | firstname2 | lastname2 | testuser2@gmail.com | test2123 | 123456789 | 0 |
Create user class: {id=20, userName=testuser1, firstname=firstname, lastname=lastname, email=testuser@gmail.com, password=test123, phoneNumber=123456789, userStatus=0}
Create user class: {id=21, userName=testuser2, firstname=firstname2, lastname=lastname2, email=testuser2@gmail.com, password=test2123, phoneNumber=123456789, userStatus=0}
When I send request to crete user with Array
Then Create user is successful with Array
And Allow to fetch the list of user details by "testuser1"
And Allow to fetch the list of user details by "testuser2"
